{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/on-click-vs-on-submit/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"조성개발실록"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dc4cfb26-857e-550c-97e8-5bdb5b760ab2","excerpt":"미안하다.. 이거 보여주려고 어그로 끌었다.. onClick vs onSubmit…","html":"<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c211b07f4714b92832fc32fa8465bcb/98b92/image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.79746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"미안하다..이거보여주려고어그로끌었다\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8c211b07f4714b92832fc32fa8465bcb/98b92/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8c211b07f4714b92832fc32fa8465bcb/c26ae/image.png 158w,\n/static/8c211b07f4714b92832fc32fa8465bcb/98b92/image.png 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>미안하다.. 이거 보여주려고 어그로 끌었다..<br>\nonClick vs onSubmit 싸움수준 ㄹㅇ실화냐?<br>\n진짜 리액트 최대의 고민이다.. 가슴이 웅장해진다<br>\n...</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>리액트에서 사용자 입력 제출할 때 뭐 쓰시나요<br>\n전 별 신경쓰지 않고 아무거나 생각나는거 쓰는 편이었는데<br>\n막상.. 생각해보니 어라? 싶어서 그냥 써보는 글입니다<br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@edidee/using-onclick-vs-onsubmit-to-submit-a-form-in-react-c7e6dd318dce\">이런 글</a>을 좀 참고했을지도?</p>\n<p>둘 다 React의 <code class=\"language-text\">useState</code>로 사용자의 입력을 관리하는 경우로 예시를 들었습니다</p>\n<h1 id=\"onclick\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#onclick\" aria-label=\"onclick permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>onClick</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">UsingClick</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setText<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onClick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Input Using onClick</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onChange</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">setText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onClick<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">제출</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>대충 이렇게 하겠죠?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 300px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4ca9f24dcd813cbe5e0c9af296602718/5a46d/image-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.69620253164557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"이게 클릭이야\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4ca9f24dcd813cbe5e0c9af296602718/5a46d/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4ca9f24dcd813cbe5e0c9af296602718/c26ae/image-1.png 158w,\n/static/4ca9f24dcd813cbe5e0c9af296602718/5a46d/image-1.png 300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그냥 간단히 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button onClick={}></code> 이렇게 쓰는 것입니다<br>\n어디서든 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button></code>을 적절한 <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code>에만 연결해주면 후속처리를 진행할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>그냥 이게 다인데..<br>\n이 <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code>은 버튼 뿐만 아니라 어디에도 <strong>범용적</strong>인 이벤트 핸들러라는 점이 특징이겠네요<br>\n그리고 <strong>클릭 핸들러</strong>로 하기 때문에, <strong>진짜 클릭해야 한다</strong>는 점입니다</p>\n<h1 id=\"onsubmit\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#onsubmit\" aria-label=\"onsubmit permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>onSubmit</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 306px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/54a58c233ee0bae6c1b169bced67ae14/98b92/image-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.79746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"결재\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/54a58c233ee0bae6c1b169bced67ae14/98b92/image-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/54a58c233ee0bae6c1b169bced67ae14/c26ae/image-2.png 158w,\n/static/54a58c233ee0bae6c1b169bced67ae14/98b92/image-2.png 306w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>아시겠지만 <code class=\"language-text\">onSubmit</code>의 경우에는 꼭 <code class=\"language-text\">form</code>으로 감싸고<br>\n버튼의 타입이 <code class=\"language-text\">type=\"submit\"</code>이어야 합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">UsingSubmit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setText<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">onSubmit</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setResult</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Input Using onSubmit</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onSubmit</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onSubmit<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onChange</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">setText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">제출</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이처럼 <code class=\"language-text\">onSubmit</code>을 써먹으려면 이를 통합 관리하는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;form></code>태그가 있어야 하고<br>\n이 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;form></code>태그에 <code class=\"language-text\">onSubmit</code>이 등록됩니다</p>\n<p>그런데 <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code>과는 좀 다른게<br>\n이렇게 제출하면 기본적으로 <strong>새로고침이 발생</strong>합니다<br>\n리액트 입장에서는 이게 state도 초기화되고 아주. 귀찮을 수 있습니다<br>\n따라서 필요한 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">onSubmit</code>함수에 인자로 들어오는 이벤트 객체 <code class=\"language-text\">e</code>를 가져다가<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">e.preventDefault()</code>과 같이 작성하여 <strong>새로고침을 방지</strong>해줍시다<br>\n그래야 <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code>과 비슷하게 쓸 수 있습니다</p>\n<p>그리고 한 가지 <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code>과 비교되는 특징은<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;form></code> 내에 속한 입력란에 포커스가 있는 채로 <strong>엔터를 눌러도 제출된다</strong>는 점입니다<br>\n이를 이용하여 굳이 클릭하지 않아도 엔터로 제출을 해결하게 할 수 있으므로<br>\n조금의 UX 개선에 도움이 될지도?</p>\n<h1 id=\"onclick-vs-onsubmit-예제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#onclick-vs-onsubmit-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"onclick vs onsubmit 예제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>onClick vs. onSubmit 예제</h1>\n<p>위에서 쓴 예제 코드 허투루 쓴게 아닙니다<br>\n오늘도 샌드박스로 좀 가져왔습니다</p>\n<iframe src=\"https://codesandbox.io/embed/4ks4yp?view=preview&module=%2Fsrc%2FUsingSubmit.jsx&hidenavigation=1\"\n     style=\"width:100%; height: 500px; border:0; border-radius: 4px; overflow:hidden;\"\n     title=\"onSubmit-vs-onClick\"\n     allow=\"accelerometer; ambient-light-sensor; camera; encrypted-media; geolocation; gyroscope; hid; microphone; midi; payment; usb; vr; xr-spatial-tracking\"\n     sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-popups allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts\"\n   ></iframe>\n<p>위에서 살펴본 차이점(<code class=\"language-text\">onSubmit</code>은 엔터로 가능함 등..)을 한번 살펴보십쇼</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"끝\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%81%9D\" aria-label=\"끝 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>끝</h1>\n<p>입니다. 진짜로<br>\n알아서 상황에 맞게 쓰면 되겠습니다</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"🗳️ 리액트 사용자 입력 : onClick 🆚 onSubmit","date":"July 07, 2024","description":"어느것을고를까요알아맞춰보세요딩동댕동커피짠","tag":["React","JavaScript"]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#onclick\">onClick</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#onsubmit\">onSubmit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#onclick-vs-onsubmit-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\">onClick vs. onSubmit 예제</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%81%9D\">끝</a></li>\n</ul>"},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/react-hooks-guide-with-examples/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🪝 리액트 훅(React Hooks) 예제와 함께 톺아보기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/geolocation-based-running-tracker-prototype/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"위치 기반 러닝 트래커 프로토타입 개발해보기"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dc4cfb26-857e-550c-97e8-5bdb5b760ab2","previousPostId":"a6b4e0db-bde5-5651-8827-65b3ba845a88","nextPostId":"a397784b-1eec-5bb1-8a08-4da4008bee4a"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}